Developer Terms of Use
des:
Propeller designs products to help improve asthma control and empower healthy, active lives. Propeller created a tool that predicts when environmental conditions are likely to impact breathing. Begin understanding your asthma conditions today.

We want to hear your comments and suggestions at help@propellerhealth.com

Disclaimer: The Propeller tool uses weather data and known patterns to provide helpful information relevant to patients with asthma, but does not provide medical advice. The tool is for informational and educational purposes only and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment, or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive actual medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial 911.
